text: Kochkildino () is a rural locality (a village) in Akbulatovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Mishkino, 4 km from Novoakbulatovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Kochkildino
